Interface CRSConnectHandler

public interface CRSConnectHandler

Implemented by the CraftARCloudRecognition class to receive the network responses from the CRSConnect.

                              int responseStatusCode,

Callback triggered once a request has completed successfully.

Parameters:
requestCode - The code corresponding to the request type has been sent. Can be checked using CRSConnect.Request.

requestFailedResponse

void requestFailedResponse(int requestCode,
                           java.lang.Exception e)
Callback triggered when a request has failed because the connection was unavailable, the server was not reached.

Parameters:
requestCode - Code identifying the request sent to the CRSConnect class Can be checked using CRSConnect.Request.
e - Exception produced in the CRSConnect when trying to perform the connection.
